        "document_type": "DATA_SHEET",
        "extracted_text": "A New Solution in Simulator-based Endoscopic Training\nNew\nSolution\nAdvanced Robotic Endoscopy Simulator for\nPrecision and Lifelike Experience\nESD EMR Handling Practice Clip Closure Suture Closure\nEndoRobotics Co., Ltd.\nwww.endorobo.com +82.2.2039.3878 +82.70.8650.3879 info@endorobo.com\n\nFeatures\nSelectable organ location in both the stomach and colon\n．\nAntrum Middle Body Colon\n． ． ．\nIncisura Angularis Cardia Rectum\n． ． ．\nUser-Friendly Interface: Intuitive touch display for seamless operation\n．\nUniversal Compatibility: Compatible with all endoscope brands and devices\n．\nEndoscope Insertion Port\n．Realistic Patient Response: Simulates breathing, random gagging, and sneezing (Stomach & Colon)\nPrecise & Efficient Robotic Control: One-touch robotic positioning for accurate\n．\nlesion targeting\nLifelike Endoscopic Functions: Realistic inflation and suction for\n．\nan authentic experience\nComprehensive Training: Basic to Advanced endoscopic therapy training is\n．\navailable for all skill levels\nSimplified Electrosurgical Connection: No ground pad needed Touchscreen-based Interface\n．\nSpecification\nDimensions [mm] 660W x 330D x 360H\nWeight [kg] 19.8\nInput 85~264VAC, 47~63Hz\nPower supply 1.4A/114VAC , 0.85A/230VAC\nOutput 24V 3.2A 76.8W\nOperating Temperature [ºC] 10 ~ 30\nDisplay Touch display 8’’ Certification KC(KR), FCC(US) , CE(EU) , RoHS (EU)\nOrdering Information\nCategory Description Order Code\nHardware EndoCubot System Unit CM-100\nStomach General CH-101\nIncisura Angularis CH-102\nHolder\nColon CH-103\nRectum CH-104 Complete Set\nER-C100\nTissue Clip CF-101\nAcc Scope Tray CA-101\nPower Cable CC-101\nStomach Tissue PTG-101\nPhantom Tissue\nColon/Rectum Tissue PTC-101\n© 2025 EndoRobotics Co., Ltd. All rights reserved. ER-EC-SM-Rev.02",
